HEADWORD: Fulgurating
<hw>Ful"gu*ra`ting</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Med.)</fld>
<def>Resembling lightning; -- used to describe intense lancinating pains
accompanying locomotor ataxy.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

